---
import Button from "../shared/Button.astro";
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
import Paragraph from "../shared/Paragraph.astro";
---

<section id="contato" class="pb-20 relative">
  <Container>
    <div
      class="w-full relative py-8 md:py-10 px-6 md:px-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-box-bg overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-full flex justify-end pointer-events-none">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 flex rounded-full relative blur-3xl opacity-60">
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob"></span>
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></span>
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 h-full w-full flex items-end pointer-events-none">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 flex rounded-full relative blur-3xl opacity-60">
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -top-1 -right-1 bg-green-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob"></span>
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -right-1 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></span>
            <span class="absolute w-16 h-16 -bottom-1 -left-1 bg-primary rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl relative z-10">
        <h1
          class="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight font-bold text-heading-1"
        >
          Vamos Construir o <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 from-20% via-primary via-30% to-green-600">Futuro</span> Juntos?
        </h1>
        
        <Paragraph className={"pt-10 text-lg"}>
          Seja um parceiro do <strong>Instituto Inspirar e Produzir</strong>. Associe sua marca a grandes eventos de Esporte, Cultura e Turismo que geram impacto social real e visibilidade em Brasília.
        </Paragraph>
        
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-md sm:max-w-xl pt-10 flex justify-center">
          <Button variant={"primary"}>
            <a href="https://wa.me/5561981534799?text=Ol%C3%A1,%20gostaria%20de%20saber%20como%20ser%20parceiro%20do%20Instituto." 
               class="text-white relative z-[5] w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-1" 
               target="_blank"
               aria-label="Iniciar conversa no WhatsApp">
               <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
                 Fale com a Nossa Equipe
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
                  </svg>
               </span>
            </a>
          </Button>
        </div>
        
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-heading-3 opacity-80">
            Junte-se a nós em projetos como o <em>Copa Pé na Areia</em> e o <em>Wake Up Brasília</em>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>